

-------- Grammar --------

rule 1 program: seps_opt
rule 2 program: seps_opt commands seps_opt
rule 3 commands: command
rule 4 commands: commands seps command
rule 5 command: words
rule 6 words: WORD
rule 7 words: words WORD
rule 8 seps_opt: 
rule 9 seps_opt: seps
rule 10 seps: sep
rule 11 seps: seps sep
rule 12 sep: ";"
rule 13 sep: NEWLINE

------- Symbols -------

**Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

  $start (5)
    on right: 
    on left : 
  program (6)
    on right: 
    on left : 1 2
  seps_opt (7)
    on right: 1 2
    on left : 8 9
  commands (8)
    on right: 2 4
    on left : 3 4
  command (9)
    on right: 3 4
    on left : 5
  seps (10)
    on right: 4 9 11
    on left : 10 11
  words (11)
    on right: 5 7
    on left : 6 7
  sep (12)
    on right: 10 11
    on left : 12 13

**Terminals, with rules where they appear

  $end (0) 
  error (1) 
  WORD (2) 6 7
  NEWLINE (3) 13
  ";" (4) 12

--------- State ---------

state 0


  NEWLINE       shift, and go to state 6
  ";"           shift, and go to state 5
  $default      reduce using rule 8 (seps_opt)

  program       go to state 1
  seps_opt      go to state 2
  seps          go to state 3
  sep           go to state 4

state 1


  $end          shift, and go to state 7


state 2

   1) program : seps_opt _
   2) program : seps_opt _ commands seps_opt

  WORD          shift, and go to state 11
  $default      reduce using rule 1 (program)

  commands      go to state 8
  command       go to state 9
  words         go to state 10

state 3

   9) seps_opt : seps _
  11) seps : seps _ sep

  NEWLINE       shift, and go to state 6
  ";"           shift, and go to state 5
  $default      reduce using rule 9 (seps_opt)

  sep           go to state 12

state 4

  10) seps : sep _

  $default      reduce using rule 10 (seps)


state 5

  12) sep : ";" _

  $default      reduce using rule 12 (sep)


state 6

  13) sep : NEWLINE _

  $default      reduce using rule 13 (sep)


state 7


  $end          shift, and go to state 13


state 8

   2) program : seps_opt commands _ seps_opt
   4) commands : commands _ seps command

  NEWLINE       shift, and go to state 6
  ";"           shift, and go to state 5
  $default      reduce using rule 8 (seps_opt)

  seps_opt      go to state 14
  seps          go to state 15
  sep           go to state 4

state 9

   3) commands : command _

  $default      reduce using rule 3 (commands)


state 10

   5) command : words _
   7) words : words _ WORD

  WORD          shift, and go to state 16
  $default      reduce using rule 5 (command)


state 11

   6) words : WORD _

  $default      reduce using rule 6 (words)


state 12

  11) seps : seps sep _

  $default      reduce using rule 11 (seps)


state 13


  $default      accept


state 14

   2) program : seps_opt commands seps_opt _

  $default      reduce using rule 2 (program)


state 15

   4) commands : commands seps _ command
   9) seps_opt : seps _
  11) seps : seps _ sep

  WORD          shift, and go to state 11
  NEWLINE       shift, and go to state 6
  ";"           shift, and go to state 5
  $default      reduce using rule 9 (seps_opt)

  command       go to state 17
  words         go to state 10
  sep           go to state 12

state 16

   7) words : words WORD _

  $default      reduce using rule 7 (words)


state 17

   4) commands : commands seps command _

  $default      reduce using rule 4 (commands)

